[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     "Nurse RN-3392 has 4 consecutive days (soft constraint violated, penalty applied)",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     "Weekend fairness deviation: max 3 weekends, min 1 weekend across staff"
